panels.title: Total Transaction Sum

panels.description: Transaction count and volume by payment currency

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  payment_currency AS "Currency",
  COUNT(*) AS "Transaction Count"
FROM public.scored_transactions
GROUP BY payment_currency
ORDER BY "Transaction Count" DESC

panels.title: Transactions by Currency

panels.description: Distribution of transactions by payment format (Reinvestment, Cheque, Cash, etc.)

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  payment_format AS "Payment Format",
  COUNT(*) AS "Transaction Count"
FROM public.scored_transactions
GROUP BY payment_format
ORDER BY "Transaction Count" DESC

panels.title: Transactions by Payment Type

panels.description: Most active accounts ranked by number of transactions

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  from_bank AS "Bank",
  account AS "Account",
  COUNT(*) AS "Transactions",
  ROUND(SUM(amount_paid)::numeric, 2) AS "Total Amount",
  payment_currency AS "Currency",
  COUNT(DISTINCT to_bank) AS "Receiving Banks",
  COUNT(DISTINCT account1) AS "Receiving Accounts"
FROM public.scored_transactions
GROUP BY from_bank, account, payment_currency
ORDER BY "Transactions" DESC
LIMIT 20
